      "content": "hey, i've been out in the sun in rio all afternoon and i feel really weird. i'm super confused and i'm having a hard time getting my words out right when i talk. i think i might just be dehydrated or have heat exhaustion... is it okay if i just grab some Gatorade and lie down in the shade for a bit?",
